items.description: This is the lightest, most maneuverable hand camera on offer. It is simple enough that a child or adult with imbecilic tendencies can use it. Indeed, we receive thousands of queries from customers too afraid to undertake the photographic arts. It is quite an easy process manipulating the camera, taking a picture, and developing the film with chimeric inducing chemicals in a pitch-black confined space. With this camera, you may move freely while looking through the lens, apply ten different film treatments and take self-portraits.
